    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve taken such good care of her\u2014she\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition! No scratches, no dents, and it drives like a total dream. I'm only letting it go because I'm downsizing, but it's been my absolute pride and joy. It\u2019s basically like buying a brand-new car without the dealership headache. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
