    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true masterpiece of automotive care, presenting in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or scratches to be found. It has been strictly garage-kept and hand-washed only. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine, factory-fresh state; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the original floor mats are spotless. Mechanically, it is flawless, featuring a complete service history from the authorized dealer and exceptionally low mileage. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity surround sound system, operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it were brand new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
