      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it runs like a total dream. You won\u2019t find a scratch on it! If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the showroom sticker price, this is your ride. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
