    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2011 Porsche Cayman S, featuring the highly desirable 3.4L flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp 6-speed manual transmission with short-throw engagement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The mid-engine chassis remains exceptionally rigid, providing neutral handling and superb lateral grip, complemented by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for optimized damping. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over vented rotors, showing zero fade. Every seal is tight, the bore scoring risk is non-existent on this generation, and the underbody is as clean as the coachwork. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning driver seeking peak analog performance.",
